      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just social media though. it feels like it's everywhere. like i'm just a joke to everyone and there's no point in trying to act like everything is okay when it isn't. it just feels like i'm stuck in a loop of being hated and i don't see how it ever actually changes. it's just tiring.",
